Interface NuSMVInput

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ModelCheckerInput, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NuSMVInputImpl

    public interface NuSMVInput
extends ModelCheckerInput
    A representation of the model object 'Nu SMV Input'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Model File Name
    • Session Script File Name
